'''Black Heather''' is a member of the leading trio of [[Bandit]]s in the [[Bandit Camp (Wilderness)|Wilderness Bandit Camp]] in levels 24-31 of the [[Wilderness]], along with [[Donny the lad]] and [[Speedy Keith]]. She, like the other two leaders, wields a [[steel scimitar]].

If players attempt to talk to her, they will receive a message stating, "''Black Heather is not interested in talking.''"

